      <item>
        <title>Meetup in Barcelona</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;One of the first series of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.meetup.com/meetup-group-RaPHYvDN/events/259065290/&quot;&gt;N26 meetups in Barcelona&lt;/a&gt;, actually the very 2nd one, where I talked about &lt;a href=&quot;https://speakerdeck.com/milan_kuveljic/mobile-test-architecture&quot;&gt;Mobile test architecture&lt;/a&gt; .
My talk was mainly about:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Automation principles&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;How to scope your automation for mobile apps&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;How to design the architecture&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;How to decide and choose tools&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;How to maintain continuous testing for mobile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
